      "warmup_inst": "Khululeka ngokuzamula, ukutjhwaba kwemilebe (brrr), kanye nokuduma okuncani isikhathi esingaba ngumzuzu. Asikho isidingo sokurekhoda — kukukhulula umphimbo wakho ngaphambi kokuvuma.",
      "vowels": "Onkamisa ahlalako",
      "vowels_inst": "Bamba unkamisa ngamunye — a, e, i, o, u — imizuzwana emi-3 ukuya kwemi-4 ngephitjhi yakho ekhululekileko, ngevolumu engaguqukiko. Lokhu kusiza u-Suno bona athathe umsindo wephimbo lakho.",
      "scales": "Isikali phezulu naphasi",
      "scales_inst": "Hlabelela isikali esilula phezulu bese wehla, ngo \"la\" nofana \"na\". Akutlhogeki bona ibe yinto epheleleko — umnqopho kukwenza imephu yebanga lakho lephimbo.",
      "section": "Isicaphuno sengoma — ingcenye 1",
      "section_inst": "Hlabelela iingoma ezi-8 ukuya kwezili-16, ngenhloso yamambala ofuna ukuyidlulisa. Beka phambili ukucaca nokuba khona phezu kokuphelela kwezobuchwepheshe.",
      "section2": "Isicaphuno sengoma — ingcenye 2",
      "section2_inst": "Hlabelela amanye amabhara ayi-8 ukuya kwayi-16 — okuhle khulu ikhorasi nofana isigaba esiphikisana nesangaphambilini. Ukuhlukahluka okunengi kusiza imodeli bona ifunde iphimbo lakho.",
      "dynamics": "Amandla: athambileko → azwakala khulu",
      "dynamics_inst": "Hlabelela umutjhwana ofanako uthoma kancani begodu uphethe ngokuzwakalako, ngaphandle kokugandelela umphimbo wakho. Lokhu kutjengisa u-Suno ububanzi bephimbo lakho.",
      "spoken": "Umutjho okhulunywako",
      "spoken_inst": "Khuluma — ungahlabeleli — umutjho omfitjhani, wemvelo, kube ngasuthi uyacoca. Lokhu kusiza u-Suno bona abone umsindo wamambala wephimbo lakho."
